    {
      "para_id": "p30",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "3. Profiling and fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 30,
      "text": "Again, both regulations, the GDPR and the DFA address this topic forming a critical area of overlap, but the DFA needs to provide the necessary clarity and broader scope:",
