    },
    {
      "para_id": "p31",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "3. Profiling and fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 31,
      "text": "GDPR coverage: In summary, the GDPR requires transparency, lawful basis, rights to object, protection mechanisms, and limitations on automated decisions for marketing profiling. Special protections apply to children profiling and the processing of special categories of personal data.",
      "char_len": 284,
      "chunk_word_count": 38,
      "ratios": {
