    {
      "para_id": "p33",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "3. Profiling and fairness"
      ],
      "ordinal": 33,
      "text": "Recommendations: The DFA should 1) address situations where consumers' data and time are monetized (requiring clear disclosure about the monetization model) or where the business model is built upon requiring personal data and attention/time in exchange for \"free\" digital services or products, 2) prevent AI-driven deceptive",
